name: edx-platform
description: To be deleted. Please use "openedx/lms" or "openedx/lms-dev" instead!
full_description:
This is the old repository for the experimental Open edX LMS docker image. It is no longer being updated. Please pull one of these images instead:
* https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/openedx/lms
* https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/openedx/lms-dev

There also exist images for the Open edX CMS:
* https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/openedx/cms
* https://hub.docker.com/repository/docker/openedx/cms-dev
